                        <interp inst="t18511124-6-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner was again <rs id="t18511124-6-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
